data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. "$15,000 PRICE REDUCTION" Welcome to Wedgewood Manor, a 55+ community located in the heart of Zephyrhills, giving the owner quick access to stores, restaurants, churches, and medical facilities. This charming and spacious 1,434 sq ft home is located on a corner lot and features 2 bedrooms and 2 baths, a 1-car garage. The roof is only 2 years old, and the siding and A/C are fairly new. The community fence provides privacy from the main road, The home has a large dining and living room (Great Room). The office/den has been used as a library and even an extra guest room at times The house features ceiling fans throughout. The master bedroom offers a spacious walk-in closet, and a master bathroom The Homeowners' Association (HOA) covers internet, cable, lawn care, and provides access to the community's central recreational center. Residents can enjoy a variety of activities, a screened-in pool, and shuffleboard facilities.  The home is being sold AS-IS
